fields.name: BULLEIT RYE SMALL BATCH WHISKEY
fields.desc: Bulleit Rye is russet in color, with rich oaky aromas. The flavor is notably smooth, with hints of vanilla, honey, and spice. Finishes crisp and clean, with long, lingering flavors.

fields.name: BULLEIT BOURBON
fields.desc: Bulliet Bourbon has a high rye content that creates a bold and spicy nose followed by hints of vanilla and honey that lead to an oaky finish.
